Ubuntu 16.04, building TF from source with CUDA, MPI, NCCL 2.2 support. I modified the code with ToString proposed fix (not sure it has been committed into the master yet). So after that error was no more I ran into this build error. I've tried bazel 0.15, 0.16

external/llvm/lib/Transforms/Scalar/JumpThreading.cpp:2165:61: warning: '((void)& BBSuccFreq +16)' may be used uninitialized in this function [-Wmaybe-uninitialized]
*std::max_element(BBSuccFreq.begin(), BBSuccFreq.end());
^
ERROR: /home/developer/tensorflow/tensorflow/BUILD:652:1: Executing genrule //tensorflow:tf_python_api_gen_v1 failed (Exit 1)
